                            <comment id="13135873" author="ocostet" created="Wed, 26 Oct 2011 11:19:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Comment from Aki Yoshida &amp;lt;elakito@googlemail.com&amp;gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Instead of going over URI, I think the code could simply use the&lt;br/&gt;
URLDecoder.decode(url.getPath(), &quot;utf-8&quot;) in the File&apos;s constructor&lt;br/&gt;
after checking url.getPath() being not null.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13136864" author="ay" created="Thu, 27 Oct 2011 07:38:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;url-decoding now applied for file path determination.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks to Oliver for analyzing this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
